<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Clearline Capital | Private Investment and Acquisition Firm</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Clearline Capital pursues founder-led businesses, select real estate, and operating partnerships through proprietary origination, disciplined underwriting, and agentic intelligence." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Clearline Capital" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="A private investment and acquisition firm pursuing off-market business acquisitions, select real estate opportunities, and operating partnerships." />
  <link rel="preload" as="image" href="/hero-clearline-1440.webp" imagesrcset="/hero-clearline-960.webp 960w, /hero-clearline-1440.webp 1440w, /hero-clearline-1920.webp 1920w" imagesizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high" />
  <style>

    :root {
      --black: #050505;
      --ink: #f7f2e8;
      --muted: rgba(247,242,232,.68);
      --soft: rgba(247,242,232,.42);
      --line: rgba(218,174,98,.28);
      --gold: #d6a85e;
      --gold2: #f0d6a0;
      --card: rgba(9,10,9,.72);
      --max: 1180px;
      --serif: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      --sans: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { margin: 0; background: var(--black); color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--sans); letter-spacing: -.01em; overflow-x: hidden; }
    body:before { content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 20; opacity: .10; background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.45) .5px, transparent .5px); background-size: 3px 3px; mix-blend-mode: overlay; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .site-nav { position: fixed; z-index: 30; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 104px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 20px clamp(20px, 4vw, 54px); background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,.70), rgba(0,0,0,0)); border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: background .28s ease, border-color .28s ease; }
    .site-nav.is-scrolled { background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5,5,5,.96), rgba(5,5,5,.9)); border-bottom-color: rgba(247,242,232,.09); }
    .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; min-width: 164px; }
    .logo img { width: 132px; height: auto; display: block; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: clamp(10px, 1.15vw, 16px); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .16em; color: rgba(247,242,232,.72); }
    .nav-links a { transition: color .25s ease; white-space: nowrap; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold2); }
    .nav-cta { border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 999px; padding: 11px 14px; color: var(--gold2) !important; background: rgba(214,168,94,.08); }
    .hero { min-height: 100svh; position: relative; display: grid; align-items: center; padding: clamp(92px, 10vh, 124px) clamp(22px, 5vw, 72px) clamp(28px, 5vh, 52px); overflow: hidden; }
    .hero-media { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; }
    .hero-media:after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,.88) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,.52) 44%, rgba(0,0,0,.20) 100%), linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,.88) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,.18) 42%, rgba(0,0,0,.54) 100%); }
    .hero-media img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center; display: block; }
    .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: var(--max); width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(310px, 360px); gap: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px); align-items: end; }
    .hero-narrative { align-self: end; padding-top: 0; }
    .eyebrow { color: var(--gold2); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .3em; font-size: clamp(12px, .95vw, 14px); margin-bottom: 14px; }
    h1, h2, h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; margin: 0; text-wrap: pretty; }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(42px, 4.45vw, 64px); line-height: .99; max-width: 780px; letter-spacing: -.055em; }
    h1 span { display: block; }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 74px); line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: -.045em; }
    .hero-copy { max-width: 710px; margin-top: 18px; color: rgba(247,242,232,.84); font-size: clamp(14px, 1.12vw, 16px); line-height: 1.5; }
    .access-card { border: 1px solid rgba(214,168,94,.34); background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(7,8,8,.88), rgba(30,23,13,.72)); box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.44); border-radius: 2px; padding: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 24px); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .access-card:before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold2), transparent); opacity: .8; }
    .access-title { font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .24em; color: var(--gold2); margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .input-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; border: 1px solid rgba(247,242,232,.18); background: rgba(0,0,0,.35); }
    .input-row input { min-width: 0; padding: 15px 14px; background: transparent; border: 0; color: var(--ink); outline: none; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .14em; }
    .input-row button { background: rgba(214,168,94,.14); color: var(--gold2); border: 0; border-left: 1px solid rgba(247,242,232,.14); padding: 0 18px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .18em; font-size: 11px; }
    .small { color: rgba(247,242,232,.55); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.55; margin-top: 14px; }
    .secondary-link { display: inline-flex; margin-top: 22px; color: var(--ink); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold); padding-bottom: 6px; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    section { padding: 104px clamp(22px, 5vw, 72px); position: relative; scroll-margin-top: 128px; }
    #firm { padding-top: clamp(72px, 8vh, 96px); }
    .wrap { max-width: var(--max); margin: 0 auto; }
    .split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .85fr 1.15fr; gap: clamp(34px, 7vw, 96px); align-items: start; }
    .lead { font-size: clamp(16px, 1.55vw, 21px); line-height: 1.58; color: rgba(247,242,232,.76); margin: 0; }
    .body { color: rgba(247,242,232,.64); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; }
    .rule { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent); opacity: .45; margin: 32px 0; }
    .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-top: 48px; }
    .card { border: 1px solid rgba(247,242,232,.12); background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255,255,255,.045), rgba(255,255,255,.015)); padding: 28px; min-height: 220px; position: relative; }
    .card:after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; border: 1px solid rgba(214,168,94,.08); transform: translate(5px, 5px); pointer-events: none; }
    .card h3 { font-size: 27px; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 22px; }
    .card p { color: rgba(247,242,232,.62); line-height: 1.68; margin: 0 0 12px; }
    .section-intro { max-width: 900px; margin-top: 24px; }
    .process-line { position: relative; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 54px; padding-top: 30px; }
    .process-line:before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; top: 10px; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(214,168,94,.78), rgba(214,168,94,.16)); }
    .process-step { position: relative; padding-right: 18px; }
    .process-step:before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -25px; left: 0; width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--gold2); box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(214,168,94,.08); }
    .process-step span { display: block; color: var(--gold2); letter-spacing: .18em; font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .process-step h3 { font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .process-step p { color: rgba(247,242,232,.62); line-height: 1.62; margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .dark-band { background: radial-gradient(circle at 18% 12%, rgba(214,168,94,.16), transparent 32%), linear-gradient(180deg, #050505, #0b0907); }
    .leadership-points { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 38px 0 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 18px 28px; }
    .leadership-points li { border-top: 1px solid rgba(214,168,94,.36); padding-top: 14px; color: rgba(247,242,232,.72); line-height: 1.55; }
    .intelligence-field-section {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 14% 18%, rgba(214,168,94,.12), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #050505 0%, #080706 52%, #050505 100%);
      overflow: clip;
    }
    .intelligence-field-shell { max-width: min(1360px, 100%); margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; }
    .intelligence-field-header { max-width: 980px; margin-bottom: clamp(34px, 5vh, 58px); }
    .intelligence-field-header .eyebrow { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .intelligence-field-header h2 { max-width: 880px; font-size: clamp(42px, 5.2vw, 78px); }
    .intelligence-field-header .lead { margin-top: 22px; max-width: 920px; }
    .intelligence-map { position: relative; min-height: clamp(560px, 62vh, 720px); border-top: 1px solid rgba(214,168,94,.16); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(214,168,94,.16); }
    .map-visual { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: visible; z-index: 1; opacity: .92; }
    .map-visual * { vector-effect: non-scaling-stroke; }
    .field-grid { opacity: .30; }
    .field-contours { opacity: .62; }
    .market-point { opacity: .62; }
    .market-point.irrelevant { opacity: .22; }
    .relationship-trace, .risk-fracture, .qualified-path, .situation-marker, .memory-return { opacity: 1; transition: opacity .45s ease, transform .55s ease; }
    .field-copy { position: relative; z-index: 3; pointer-events: none; }
    .field-labels, .capability-labels, .qualified-final { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 2; }
    .field-label, .capability-label { position: absolute; color: var(--field-muted, rgba(247,242,232,.66)); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: .88; }
    .field-label.emphasis, .capability-label.emphasis { color: var(--gold2); }
    .capability-label { color: rgba(247,242,232,.78); font-weight: 600; }
    .capability-label:before { content: ''; display: inline-block; width: 16px; height: 1px; margin: 0 8px 4px 0; background: var(--gold); opacity: .72; }
    .qualified-card { position: absolute; right: clamp(22px, 6vw, 86px); bottom: clamp(38px, 8vh, 96px); width: min(420px, 34vw); padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 38px); background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8,7,6,.96), rgba(17,14,10,.94)); border-top: 2px solid rgba(240,214,160,.84); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(240,214,160,.84); box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.46); }
    .qualified-card h3 { font-size: clamp(28px, 3.4vw, 52px); line-height: .96; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -.03em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .qualified-card p { margin: 0; color: rgba(247,242,232,.76); font-size: clamp(14px, 1.3vw, 17px); line-height: 1.45; }
    .governance-note { max-width: 760px; margin: clamp(24px, 4vh, 40px) 0 0 auto; color: rgba(247,242,232,.62); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .intelligence-field-section:not(.is-visible) .capability-label,
    .intelligence-field-section:not(.is-visible) .qualified-card,
    .intelligence-field-section:not(.is-visible) .qualified-path,
    .intelligence-field-section:not(.is-visible) .situation-marker { opacity: .18; }
    .intelligence-field-section.is-visible .capability-label { animation: resolveIn .8s ease both; }
    .intelligence-field-section.is-visible .qualified-card { animation: resolveIn .9s ease .18s both; }
    @keyframes resolveIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    .mobile-field-copy { display: none; }
    .intelligence-reduced-copy { position: absolute; left: -9999px; }
    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .intelligence-field-section { padding: 84px 20px 72px; }
      .intelligence-field-header h2 { font-size: clamp(38px, 10vw, 72px); }
      .intelligence-map { min-height: auto; border: 0; }
      .map-visual.desktop-map, .field-labels, .capability-labels, .qualified-final { display: none; }
      .map-visual.mobile-map { display: block; position: absolute; inset: 168px 0 auto 0; height: 540px; opacity: .74; }
      .mobile-field-copy { display: block; position: relative; z-index: 3; }
      .mobile-field-step { margin: 0 0 30px; max-width: 330px; }
      .mobile-field-step:nth-child(2) { margin-left: auto; }
      .mobile-field-step h3 { font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.08; margin-bottom: 9px; }
      .mobile-field-step p { margin: 0; color: rgba(247,242,232,.68); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; }
      .mobile-qualified-card { margin-top: 34px; padding: 26px 22px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8,7,6,.96), rgba(17,14,10,.94)); border-top: 2px solid rgba(240,214,160,.84); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(240,214,160,.84); }
      .mobile-qualified-card h3 { font-size: clamp(30px, 8.5vw, 43px); line-height: .95; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
      .mobile-qualified-card p { margin: 0; color: rgba(247,242,232,.76); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }
      .governance-note { margin: 26px 0 0; font-size: 13px; }
    }
    @media (min-width: 981px) { .map-visual.mobile-map { display: none; } }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      * { animation: none !important; transition: none !important; scroll-behavior: auto !important; }
      .intelligence-field-section:not(.is-visible) .capability-label,
      .intelligence-field-section:not(.is-visible) .qualified-card,
      .intelligence-field-section:not(.is-visible) .qualified-path,
      .intelligence-field-section:not(.is-visible) .situation-marker { opacity: 1; }
    }

    .access-section { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #050505, #090705); }
    .hidden { display: none; }
    .form-shell { margin-top: 36px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .field, textarea { border: 1px solid rgba(247,242,232,.13); background: rgba(247,242,232,.035); padding: 15px 14px; color: var(--ink); min-height: 52px; font: inherit; outline: none; }
    textarea { grid-column: 1 / -1; min-height: 122px; resize: vertical; }
    .submit { grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-self: start; border: 1px solid rgba(214,168,94,.42); background: rgba(214,168,94,.12); color: var(--gold2); padding: 14px 22px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .18em; font-size: 12px; }
    footer { padding: 48px clamp(22px, 5vw, 72px); border-top: 1px solid rgba(247,242,232,.1); color: rgba(247,242,232,.62); }
    footer .wrap { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 20px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    @media (max-width: 1180px) { .nav-links { gap: 10px; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .12em; } .logo { min-width: 132px; } }
    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-inner, .split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-narrative { padding-top: 0; }
      .access-card { max-width: 480px; }
      .cards, .leadership-points { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .process-line { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0; margin-top: 42px; padding: 0 0 0 24px; }
      .process-line:before { left: 4px; right: auto; top: 2px; bottom: 6px; width: 1px; height: auto; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(214,168,94,.78), rgba(214,168,94,.16)); }
      .process-step { padding: 0 0 28px; }
      .process-step:before { top: 3px; left: -24px; width: 8px; height: 8px; }
      .process-step span { margin-bottom: 8px; }
      .process-step h3 { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
      .process-step p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.55; max-width: 620px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 620px) {
      .site-nav { position: sticky; height: 72px; padding: 8px 18px 7px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,.96), rgba(0,0,0,.86)); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(247,242,232,.08); }
      .logo img { width: 98px; }
      .hero { min-height: calc(100svh - 72px); padding: 28px 20px 26px; }
      .hero-inner { gap: 22px; }
      .hero-copy { margin-top: 14px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.42; }
      .hero .secondary-link { margin-top: 16px; }
      .access-card { padding: 17px; }
      .access-title { margin-bottom: 12px; }
      .input-row input { padding: 12px 11px; }
      .input-row button { padding: 0 12px; }
      .small { margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.42; }
      section { padding: 72px 20px; scroll-margin-top: 96px; }
      .form-shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      textarea, .submit { grid-column: auto; }
      h1 { font-size: clamp(37px, 11.3vw, 44px); line-height: .98; }
      footer .wrap { flex-direction: column; }
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      * { animation: none !important; scroll-behavior: auto !important; }
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
    <a class="logo" href="#top" aria-label="Clearline Capital home"><img src="/logo-white-132.webp" srcset="/logo-white-132.webp 132w, /logo-white-264.webp 264w" sizes="132px" width="132" height="83" alt="Clearline Capital" /></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#firm">Firm</a>
      <a href="#focus">Investment Focus</a>
      <a href="#process">Process</a>
      <a href="#network">Network</a>
      <a href="#intelligence">Intelligence</a>
      <a href="#access" class="nav-cta">Request Consideration</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main id="top">
    <header class="hero">
      <picture class="hero-media" aria-hidden="true">
        <source type="image/avif" srcset="/hero-clearline-960.avif 960w, /hero-clearline-1440.avif 1440w, /hero-clearline-1920.avif 1920w" sizes="100vw" />
        <source type="image/webp" srcset="/hero-clearline-960.webp 960w, /hero-clearline-1440.webp 1440w, /hero-clearline-1920.webp 1920w" sizes="100vw" />
        <img src="/hero-clearline-1440.webp" srcset="/hero-clearline-960.webp 960w, /hero-clearline-1440.webp 1440w, /hero-clearline-1920.webp 1920w" sizes="100vw" width="1440" height="810" alt="" fetchpriority="high" decoding="sync" />
      </picture>
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-narrative">
          <div class="eyebrow">PRIVATE INVESTMENT AND ACQUISITION FIRM</div>
          <h1>Off-market acquisitions, informed by proprietary intelligence.</h1>
          <p class="hero-copy">Clearline Capital pursues founder-led businesses, select real estate, and operating partnerships through direct relationships, disciplined underwriting, and a purpose-built agentic intelligence platform that expands the firm’s off-market origination and research capabilities.</p>
          <a class="secondary-link" href="#firm">Enter the overview</a>
        </div>
        <aside class="access-card" aria-label="Invitation access validation">
          <div class="access-title">Invitation access</div>
          <div class="input-row">
            <input id="invite-code" aria-label="Invitation code" placeholder="Invitation code" autocomplete="off" />
            <button id="invite-submit" type="button">Submit</button>
          </div>
          <p class="small">Access is reserved for relevant opportunities and trusted introductions.</p>
          <a class="secondary-link" href="#access">Request consideration</a>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section id="firm">
      <div class="wrap split">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">THE FIRM</div>
          <h2>A disciplined platform for off-market acquisitions.</h2>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="lead">Clearline Capital identifies and evaluates select businesses, real estate, and operating partnerships outside broadly marketed channels.</p>
          <div class="rule"></div>
          <p class="body">The firm combines sector research, proprietary market intelligence, and experienced investor and operator perspective to develop conviction around a limited number of qualified situations.</p>
          <p class="body">Each opportunity is tested through financial analysis, professional diligence, operating insight, and a clearly defined path to execution.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="focus">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="eyebrow">INVESTMENT FOCUS</div>
        <h2>Where Clearline Capital invests.</h2>
        <div class="cards">
          <article class="card"><h3>Founder-led and privately held businesses</h3><p>Companies facing succession, expansion, recapitalization, or ownership transition, with current interest in aesthetics, wellness, healthcare services, and other durable service categories.</p></article>
          <article class="card"><h3>Select real estate opportunities</h3><p>Properties, portfolios, and operating real estate where basis, repositioning potential, or ownership complexity creates a compelling investment thesis.</p></article>
          <article class="card"><h3>Operating partnerships</h3><p>Partnerships with experienced operators and sector specialists where resources and execution capability can accelerate growth or strategic improvement.</p></article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="process" class="dark-band">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="eyebrow">HOW OPPORTUNITIES ADVANCE</div>
        <h2>A disciplined path from origination to decision.</h2>
        <p class="lead section-intro">Every situation moves through a controlled investment process that separates market interest from actionable conviction.</p>
        <div class="process-line" aria-label="Clearline Capital opportunity process">
          <article class="process-step"><span>01</span><h3>Originate</h3><p>The firm develops potential situations through proprietary intelligence, sector research, trusted referrals, and operator insight.</p></article>
          <article class="process-step"><span>02</span><h3>Qualify</h3><p>Business or asset quality, ownership context, sector dynamics, strategic relevance, and seller objectives are tested against the mandate.</p></article>
          <article class="process-step"><span>03</span><h3>Underwrite</h3><p>Qualified situations advance through financial analysis, operating review, risk assessment, transaction design, and financing plans.</p></article>
          <article class="process-step"><span>04</span><h3>Validate</h3><p>Relevant advisors, operators, and specialists examine the thesis through professional diligence and scenario review.</p></article>
          <article class="process-step"><span>05</span><h3>Decide</h3><p>Clearline Capital proceeds only when the evidence, economics, and execution plan support investment conviction.</p></article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="network">
      <div class="wrap split">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">NETWORK AND GOVERNANCE</div>
          <h2>Experienced perspective. Clear authority.</h2>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="lead">Clearline Capital operates through a private network of investors, founders, operators, advisors, and funding partners. The network contributes sector knowledge, operating experience, transaction perspective, and relevant resources to select situations.</p>
          <div class="rule"></div>
          <p class="body">Opportunities are evaluated through disciplined underwriting, professional diligence, and clearly defined investment governance.</p>
          <ul class="leadership-points">
            <li>Experienced investor and operator perspective.</li>
            <li>Independent professional diligence.</li>
            <li>Disciplined resource allocation.</li>
            <li>Defined investment governance.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="intelligence" class="intelligence-field-section" aria-labelledby="intelligence-title">
      <div class="intelligence-field-shell">
        <div class="intelligence-field-header">
