          <p class="body">Submissions are screened for mandate fit, source quality, and strategic relevance. Only qualified matters advance.</p>
          <form name="access-request" method="POST" action="/thank-you" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" class="form-shell">
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="access-request" />
