            <input class="field" name="email" type="email" placeholder="Email" aria-label="Email" required />
            <input class="field" name="company" placeholder="Company" aria-label="Company" />
            <input class="field" name="referred-by" placeholder="Referred by" aria-label="Referred by" required />
            <textarea name="context" placeholder="Brief context" aria-label="Brief context" required></textarea>
            <button class="submit" type="submit">Request Consideration</button>
          </form>
          <p class="small">Nothing on this page is an offer to sell securities or a solicitation to buy securities. Clearline Capital evaluates opportunities privately and selectively. Any investment, acquisition, partnership, or transaction activity is subject to independent review, diligence, documentation, professional advice, and final approval by the appropriate parties.</p>
